sg":"<blockquote>你個標題會唔會引到著名會員「哲學撚」入黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n已經入咗嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1c05985d990e0efcb180960e949642a00a9c5cc","tid":237131,"uid":37093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T22:33:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>之前買左本叫自願被吃的豬 都唔錯 啟發到你不停思考</blockquote><br />\n得閒去書局睇下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />thanks"},{"pid":"44d8234d8ec61d929e8899bc8e15aff17360377e","tid":237131,"uid":28181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T22:47:27.000Z","msg":"楊天命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e77eba1f6bbaddb729e39e979c836cc332a8949","tid":237131,"uid":112769,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T17:59:41.000Z","msg":"入口級（依d可以幫你了解到哲學係諗d咩問題）<br />\n<br />\n哲學問題 羅素<br />\n哲學概論 冀劍制<br />\nIntroduction to Philosophy.  Peter K.Mclnerny<br />\n圖解實用倫理學/政治哲學 梁光耀<br />\nAn Introduction to Political Philosophy. Jonathan Wolff<br />\n李天命的思考方法 李天命<br />\n語理分析的思考方法 李天命<br />\n思方導航-批判思考導論 貝剛毅<br />\n知識論 鄺芷人<br />\n死亡 Shelly Kagan<br />\n當代西方意識哲學的概念革命-心靈風暴 冀劍制<br />\n政治的道德 周保松<br />\nJustice What's the right thing to do?  Michael J. Sandel <br />\n（如果你係想係香港讀哲學 建議你睇思方學的書先 因為香港主流係分析哲學 思方學係基本的工具 其實日常生活都好有用 由其是邏輯謬誤！）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n進階就考慮 鐘意諗咩問題多d<br />\n再諗睇咩書<br />\n <br />\n如果你興趣係 倫理學 道德哲學 政治哲學就睇 <br />\n正義論 John Rawls (左翼自由主義）<br />\n政治自由主義 （同上）<br />\n作為公平的正義 （同上）<br />\n無政府 烏托幫 及 XXX (唔記得個人同書名 有關自由主義的書黎）<br />\nAfter virtue （唔記得作者 有關社群主義）<br />\n正義諸領域 （同上）<br />\n論自由 J.S Mill <br />\n理想國 柏拉圖<br />\n共產黨宣言 馬克斯<br />\n功利主義 J.S Mill<br />\n動物解放 Peter Singer （動物權利）<br />\n自由人的平等政治 周保松 （你當正義論的解讀 但係我會建議你睇原著）<br />\n康德三大集 （自己搵 唔記得名）<br />\n亞里士多德  （三本倫理學書 自己搵）<br />\n論語 孔子<br />\n<br />\n其他的範疇你要搵其他巴打<br />\n（依堆都有排你磨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）"},{"pid":"09f34179fb349c8b33f9181017a5c3957843e1ef","tid":237131,"uid":112769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T18:01:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>有時間想去圖書館搵哲學書睇 <br />\n想問下有咩入門書推介？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你有冇睇過邊本先？</blockquote><br />\n冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />淨係今日睇咗少少尼采新論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n尼彩真係好嘔心 好難明 唔岩入門睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eaac322689d4632aa72f9aded9fc6e8a5eca7710","tid":237131,"uid":6464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T18:03:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>有時間想去圖書館搵哲學書睇 <br />\n想問下有咩入門書推介？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你有冇睇過邊本先？</blockquote><br />\n冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />淨係今日睇咗少少尼采新論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n尼彩真係好嘔心 好難明 唔岩入門睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n尼采直頭係難頂<br />\n未理解到佢思維<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3150b09cf0c963fb293396c57affd4997cfc560c","tid":237131,"uid":112769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T18:10:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>睇英文哲學書好快放棄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我英文廢應該會睇到眼都凸埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打...我認真同你講<br />\n如果你英文唔好 但有心學或修讀哲學<br />\n你要有心理準備 比人用多n倍時間<br />\n有一個解決辦法睇中文翻譯<br />\n但一定唔好 翻得好差<br />\n好似一個字Goods 依個字 不同哲學家有不同用法<br />\n唔係讀哲學的人翻譯依個字會釋到on99<br />\n英文好 好緊要<br />\n<br />\n利申：我係人板 會考中英U 依加讀緊有關哲學的MA<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c909b59726dd3bdf535734a8b39169491b47d6a1","tid":237131,"uid":112769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T18:12:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />淨係今日睇咗少少尼采新論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n尼彩真係好嘔心 好難明 唔岩入門睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n尼采直頭係難頂<br />\n未理解到佢思維<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我到依加都未有勇氣再拎黎睇<br />\n我覺得睇得明 尼彩 黑格爾 的人都係神人<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n完全唔係for人睇的野黎"},{"pid":"1b72988d54bfa0ba867bc44639d88e7bf0bde946","tid":237131,"uid":12984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T18:13:41.000Z","msg":"左膠最推崇既theory of justice<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c964df81fffd85706ec5eb4ef99165725e1d029","tid":237131,"uid":112769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T18:15:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>左膠最推崇既theory of justice<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n直頭係左膠聖經<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"564241558ffd6278b05febbc00b6c3aceba084c4","tid":237131,"uid":14090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T18:16:47.000Z","msg":"Theory of justice個堆囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a538bf751dd819a7ae224d679cd6276cee00a59d","tid":237131,"uid":8883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T05:48:34.000Z","msg":"點解會有人當A Theory of Justice係入門書<br />\n就算想睇Rawls 一係睇其他人寫既介紹<br />\n一係睇佢本Restatement<br />\n將TJ推介俾初學者根本就係不負責任既講法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cba34654d8ddc5ca236bc221b1929c2dd792d923","tid":237131,"uid":14090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T14:48:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解會有人當A Theory of Justice係入門書<br />\n就算想睇Rawls 一係睇其他人寫既介紹<br />\n一係睇佢本Restatement<br />\n將TJ推介俾初學者根本就係不負責任既講法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\ntheory of justice唔難明 易睇 又解釋詳盡 有幾不負責任? <br />\n介紹本書要負咩責任?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f32da99af818ff4f57b0a0b669de94139ca979ae","tid":237131,"uid":37093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T16:23:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>睇英文哲學書好快放棄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我英文廢應該會睇到眼都凸埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打...我認真同你講<br />\n如果你英文唔好 但有心學或修讀哲學<br />\n你要有心理準備 比人用多n倍時間<br />\n有一個解決辦法睇中文翻譯<br />\n但一定唔好 翻得好差<br />\n好似一個字Goods 依個字 不同哲學家有不同用法<br />\n唔係讀哲學的人翻譯依個字會釋到on99<br />\n英文好 好緊要<br />\n<br />\n利申：我係人板 會考中英U 依加讀緊有關哲學的MA<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我唔係想修讀哲學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />只係覺得幾有趣想睇下學下 我覺得讀哲學可以幫到人諗嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3cc5b807d915d1b9dbbd9d71a040adbfe01927a","tid":237131,"uid":37093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T16:25:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />淨係今日睇咗少少尼采新論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n尼彩真係好嘔心 好難明 唔岩入門睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n尼采直頭係難頂<br />\n未理解到佢思維<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我到依加都未有勇氣再拎黎睇<br />\n我覺得睇得明 尼彩 黑格爾 的人都係神人<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n完全唔係for人睇的野黎</blockquote><br />\n我都唔係幾睇得明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />淨係知佢唔by栢拉圖嗰套<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />不過佢屌基督教嗰啲論點好正"},{"pid":"e6fffb728a847cadb80b35d21ba148278393b258","tid":237131,"uid":35364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T16:34:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />淨係今日睇咗少少尼采新論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n尼彩真係好嘔心 好難明 唔岩入門睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n尼采直頭係難頂<br />\n未理解到佢思維<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我到依加都未有勇氣再拎黎睇<br />\n我覺得睇得明 尼彩 黑格爾 的人都係神人<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n完全唔係for人睇的野黎</blockquote><br />\n我都唔係幾睇得明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />淨係知佢唔by栢拉圖嗰套<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />不過佢屌基督教嗰啲論點好正</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n尼采批評基督教，唔係批評宗教本身<br />\n最主要係批判班信徒<br />\n尼采其實比信徒更有宗教狂熱"},{"pid":"445957620ee0c676dc068eb719158479306b31ac","tid":237131,"uid":37093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T17:52:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>入口級（依d可以幫你了解到哲學係諗d咩問題）<br />\n<br />\n哲學問題 羅素<br />\n哲學概論 冀劍制<br />\nIntroduction to Philosophy.  Peter K.Mclnerny<br />\n圖解實用倫理學/政治哲學 梁光耀<br />\nAn Introduction to Political Philosophy. Jonathan Wolff<br />\n李天命的思考方法 李天命<br />\n語理分析的思考方法 李天命<br />\n思方導航-批判思考導論 貝剛毅<br />\n知識論 鄺芷人<br />\n死亡 Shelly Kagan<br />\n當代西方意識哲學的概念革命-心靈風暴 冀劍制<br />\n政治的道德 周保松<br />\nJustice What's the right thing to do?  Michael J. Sandel <br />\n（如果你係想係香港讀哲學 建議你睇思方學的書先 因為香港主流係分析哲學 思方學係基本的工具 其實日常生活都好有用 由其是邏輯謬誤！）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n進階就考慮 鐘意諗咩問題多d<br />\n再諗睇咩書<br />\n <br />\n如果你興趣係 倫理學 道德哲學 政治哲學就睇 <br />\n正義論 John Rawls (左翼自由主義）<br />\n政治自由主義 （同上）<br />\n作為公平的正義 （同上）<br />\n無政府 烏托幫 及 XXX (唔記得個人同書名 有關自由主義的書黎）<br />\nAfter virtue （唔記得作者 有關社群主義）<br />\n正義諸領域 （同上）<br />\n論自由 J.S Mill <br />\n理想國 柏拉圖<br />\n共產黨宣言 馬克斯<br />\n功利主義 J.S Mill<br />\n動物解放 Peter Singer （動物權利）<br />\n自由人的平等政治 周保松 （你當正義論的解讀 但係我會建議你睇原著）<br />\n康德三大集 （自己搵 唔記得名）<br />\n亞里士多德  （三本倫理學書 自己搵）<br />\n論語 孔子<br />\n<br />\n其他的範疇你要搵其他巴打<br />\n（依堆都有排你磨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2fb8f310b7133593bf203912b43bb88933bb79d4","tid":237131,"uid":11311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T17:54:53.000Z","msg":"最近有本圖解100個哲學概念定咩"},{"pid":"0235dbd00e9559c9908d4ec597617662eb13d608","tid":237131,"uid":37093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T18:05:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />淨係今日睇咗少少尼采新論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n尼彩真係好嘔心 好難明 唔岩入門睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n尼采直頭係難頂<br />\n未理解到佢思維<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我到依加都未有勇氣再拎黎睇<br />\n我覺得睇得明 尼彩 黑格爾 的人都係神人<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n完全唔係for人睇的野黎</blockquote><br />\n我都唔係幾睇得明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />淨係知佢唔by栢拉圖嗰套<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />不過佢屌基督教嗰啲論點好正</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n尼采批評基督教，唔係批評宗教本身<br />\n最主要係批判班信徒<br />\n尼采其實比信徒更有宗教狂熱</blockquote><br />\n我嘅理解係佢覺得班信徒曲解咗耶穌嘅教義<br />\n淨係一味盲目承襲佢嘅教義但係失去咗好似耶穌嗰種反抗傳統嘅精神 <br />\n又用基督教嘅名義作惡賺錢 仲要勁矛盾咁一方面講到要愛世人一面又用佢地嘅所謂教義審判人<br />\n佢好似仲有屌基督教勁多嘢都係FF出嚟仲要promote憐憫嘅思想<br />\n好似係 唔知有冇get錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23a62388f1bbbbdbd2b819b46735d3f7ef128ff8","tid":237131,"uid":37093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T18:06:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>最近有本圖解100個哲學概念定咩</blockquote><br />\n圖解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />啱我"},{"pid":"4e3a1d64762234ce218478ddae15b66362ddfe55","tid":237131,"uid":8883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T18:24:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>點解會有人當A Theory of Justice係入門書<br />\n就算想睇Rawls 一係睇其他人寫既介紹<br />\n一係睇佢本Restatement<br />\n將TJ推介俾初學者根本就係不負責任既講法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\ntheory of justice唔難明 易睇 又解釋詳盡 有幾不負責任? <br />\n介紹本書要負咩責任?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔係想引罵戰<br />\n但你係講緊Rawls既A Theory of Justice<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a983dc6d9e345f932f3f58c4577427ac9ea672cf","tid":237131,"uid":8883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T18:26:17.000Z","msg":"無政府 烏托幫 及 XXX (唔記得個人同書名 有關自由主義的書黎）<br />\n<br />\nNozick既Anarchy, State and Utopia<br />\ndefend libertarianism同回應Rawls既重要著作之一"},{"pid":"c488fadc4b22be87a670efd08fb9e3999412dd9c","tid":237131,"uid":35870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T00:56:51.000Z","msg":"之前有條友教落，類似黑格爾尼采呢d應該要買多本介紹尼采嘅書一齊睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n原文同介紹兩本一齊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同埋個條友話，千其唔好睇中國人寫嘅哲學書，全部都係左抄右抄，要睇就睇香港人，因為香港人有d都叫德國留學返黎<br />\n<br />\n重點係講呢d野條友係大陸人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0181add9f66dfce3870ff6c7ced6f37257b60d7","tid":237131,"uid":34300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T01:03:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>睇英文哲學書好快放棄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我英文廢應該會睇到眼都凸埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打...我認真同你講<br />\n如果你英文唔好 但有心學或修讀哲學<br />\n你要有心理準備 比人用多n倍時間<br />\n有一個解決辦法睇中文翻譯<br />\n但一定唔好 翻得好差<br />\n好似一個字Goods 依個字 不同哲學家有不同用法<br />\n唔係讀哲學的人翻譯依個字會釋到on99<br />\n英文好 好緊要<br />\n<br />\n利申：我係人板 會考中英U 依加讀緊有關哲學的MA<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n中大?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4de49eacaf70d7195c5e7963a0a8e0dca582075d","tid":237131,"uid":112769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T12:30:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n我英文廢應該會睇到眼都凸埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打...我認真同你講<br />\n如果你英文唔好 但有心學或修讀哲學<br />\n你要有心理準備 比人用多n倍時間<br />\n有一個解決辦法睇中文翻譯<br />\n但一定唔好 翻得好差<br />\n好似一個字Goods 依個字 不同哲學家有不同用法<br />\n唔係讀哲學的人翻譯依個字會釋到on99<br />\n英文好 好緊要<br />\n<br />\n利申：我係人板 會考中英U 依加讀緊有關哲學的MA<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n中大?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n全香港得兩三間有哲學有關的MA<br />\n我講邊間咪姐係自爆&mdash;_&mdash;"},{"pid":"6ea69094f9b5c1a9accb0c935f3d5ceee2d14eb3","tid":237131,"uid":2438,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T12:35:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 正想話真有此人"},{"pid":"1c94ac3fad1300564bf99ad52a1d555f19c087b3","tid":237131,"uid":112769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T12:35:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>之前有條友教落，類似黑格爾尼采呢d應該要買多本介紹尼采嘅書一齊睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n原文同介紹兩本一齊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同埋個條友話，千其唔好睇中國人寫嘅哲學書，全部都係左抄右抄，要睇就睇香港人，因為香港人有d都叫德國留學返黎<br />\n<br />\n重點係講呢d野條友係大陸人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n中國大陸的人好多都亂黎.....<br />\n得個抄字...你一睇佢地的論文期刊就知...<br />\n台灣的哲學發展得比香港前<br />\n學術上黎講 睇台灣同香港都ok<br />\n大陸就<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n大陸有部分都ok的...<br />\n同香港哲學教授有關係一齊出過書的都正常的<br />\n（TA話真心追求真理的 唔理政治野 北京大學is ok)"},{"pid":"13d1bbca3494b1353c2b91497ab94e1ab5cc4b08","tid":237131,"uid":2438,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T12:38:49.000Z","msg":"放棄接觸哲學啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 垃圾科，嚴重傷害大腦"},{"pid":"6bb7fce726428a87addaf16bd0eec0077108b796","tid":237131,"uid":112769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T12:41:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>點解會有人當A Theory of Justice係入門書<br />\n就算想睇Rawls 一係睇其他人寫既介紹<br />\n一係睇佢本Restatement<br />\n將TJ推介俾初學者根本就係不負責任既講法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\ntheory of justice唔難明 易睇 又解釋詳盡 有幾不負責任? <br />\n介紹本書要負咩責任?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔係想引罵戰<br />\n但你係講緊Rawls既A Theory of Justice<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我當時係睇左 周保松本 自由人的平等政治<br />\n再去睇正義論 A Theory of Justice 中文版 先捉到佢套邏輯<br />\n如果叫我一開始就食本Justice<br />\n如果我又冇學過康德倫理學（義務論）我諗我會睇唔明條油up甩鳩野<br />\n因為佢個理論 建構係康德 rational being的概念之上 好核心的地方黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76ffb605ee63a968b7cbc5236c7b3aa8d8e6ffbb","tid":237131,"uid":112769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T12:42:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>放棄接觸哲學啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 垃圾科，嚴重傷害大腦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nNoted with thanks"}]}